## Primary Services

### ELOPAY India (INR)
Accept UPI, IMPS, NEFT, RTGS payments in Indian Rupees with instant settlements.

### ELOPAY Pakistan (PKR)
Accept JazzCash, EasyPaisa, bank transfers in Pakistani Rupees.

### ELOPAY Bangladesh (BDT)
Accept bKash, Nagad, Rocket payments in Bangladeshi Taka.

### ELOPAY Crypto (USDT)
Accept USDT Tether stablecoin payments globally.

